A Rutted Road~
   The wars against the evil races have left their mark upon the
land as well as the people. Here at Fateful Falls one can see the
marks of this. Trees, those still standing, have arrows embedded
within their bark, spots of black where fire scored but did not kill.
The ground is littered with the odd broken buckle that once held
swords secure to a warriors belt or a shield that was shattered by
a massive blow. The rutted road leads eastward toward the village.
